    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty car! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me and is still in really solid shape. It runs smoothly, looks great, and is totally ready for its next adventure with you! I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic deal on a car that still has so much life left in it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 29900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
