      "description": "Presenting a vehicle that exemplifies mechanical reliability and consistent performance. This unit has been maintained to a high standard, ensuring all primary systems operate with precision and efficiency. It offers a sophisticated driving experience for those seeking a dependable, high-value asset that maintains its structural and aesthetic integrity. We invite you to inspect this well-appointed selection, which stands as a testament to enduring quality and professional care.",
      "price": 28900.0,
